                <ul class="service-features">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> RESTful API Development</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Microservices Architecture</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Database Design & Optimization</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Unit Testing & TDD</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">
                    <i class="fab fa-angular"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Angular Development</h3>
                <p>Creating modern, responsive, and interactive web applications using Angular with TypeScript and best practices.</p>
                <ul class="service-features">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Single Page Applications</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Component-Based Architecture</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> State Management</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Responsive UI/UX</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Full-Stack Solutions</h3>
                <p>End-to-end application development combining .NET backend with Angular frontend for complete business solutions.</p>
                <ul class="service-features">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Complete Web Applications</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> API Integration</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Authentication & Authorization</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Deployment & DevOps</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-database"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Database Solutions</h3>
                <p>Designing and optimizing database schemas with MS SQL Server, PostgreSQL, and MongoDB for efficient data management.</p>
                <ul class="service-features">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Database Design</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Query Optimization</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Stored Procedures</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Data Migration</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Technical Consulting</h3>
                <p>Providing expert guidance on architecture decisions, code reviews, and best practices for .NET and Angular projects.</p>
                <ul class="service-features">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Code Review</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Architecture Planning</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Performance Optimization</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Team Mentoring</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">
                    <i class="fab fa-docker"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>DevOps & Deployment</h3>
                <p>Containerization, CI/CD pipeline setup, and deployment strategies using Docker and modern DevOps practices.</p>
                <ul class="service-features">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Docker Containerization</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> CI/CD Pipelines</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Cloud Deployment</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Monitoring & Logging</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
